definitions.definition: Within any limits, enclosure, or substance; inside; internal; inner.
examples: the interior apartments of a house; the interior surface of a hollow ball

definitions.definition: Remote from the limits, frontier, or shore; inland.
examples: the interior parts of a region or country

main_definition: Within any limits, enclosure, or substance; inside; internal; inner.
secondary_definitions: Remote from the limits, frontier, or shore; inland.
